author: A Correspondent
title: Cricket tourney for ICSE, ISC schools
text:
An inter-school cricket tournament for ICSE & ISC schools is being held at the Oval Maidan and will conclude on October 9.
As many as 46 teams from all over Maharashtra are participating in this event. The best 16 players from the tournament will represent Maharashtra in the ICSE National level tournament to be held in Lucknow later this month.
